-- Mauritius Leasing Shares Retreat to Lowest Level in Four Months
-- B y   K a m l e s h   B h u c k o r y
-- 2012-02-27T10:05:43Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-02-27/mauritius-leasing-shares-retreat-to-lowest-level-in-four-months.html
Mauritius Leasing Co. Ltd, which
provides leasing facilities for movable assets and equipment,
fell to the lowest level since October.  The stock retreated a second day, dropping 9.5 percent to
6.70 rupees by the end of trading in  Port Louis , the capital,
the weakest close since Oct. 21.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Kamlesh Bhuckory in Port Louis at 
 kbhuckory@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
